# UI Design Principles
- Always default to a "High Density" design style.
- Use smaller fonts: base text should be `text-sm` (14px) or `text-[13px]`.
- Use Shadcn UI components with `size="sm"` by default.
- Prefer borders over shadows for depth.
- Border radius should be `rounded-md` (6px) or `rounded-sm` (4px), rarely `rounded-xl`.

# Tech Stack & Patterns
- React + Tailwind CSS.
- Icons: Lucide React (size 14-16px).
- Theming: `next-themes` (if Next.js) or standard CSS variables for Dark Mode.
- I18n: Use `react-i18next` patterns. Never hardcode strings.
